comment: /**  * Returns {@link ProxyAsyncConfiguration} or {@code AspectJAsyncConfiguration}  * for {@code PROXY} and {@code ASPECTJ} values of {@link EnableAsync#mode()},  * respectively.  */
code: /**  * Returns {@link ProxyAsyncConfiguration} or {@code AspectJAsyncConfiguration}  * for {@code PROXY} and {@code ASPECTJ} values of {@link EnableAsync#mode()},  * respectively.  */ @Override @Nullable public String[] selectImports(AdviceMode adviceMode) {     switch(adviceMode) {         case PROXY:             return new String[] { ProxyAsyncConfiguration.class.getName() }.         case ASPECTJ:             return new String[] { ASYNC_EXECUTION_ASPECT_CONFIGURATION_CLASS_NAME }.         default:             return null.     } }
